Package: startProject
Type: Package
Title: Create a Project Directory and Templates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rocio", "Lopez", email = "Rocio.LopezMoscoso@cuanschutz.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package has several functions to create a project directory 
    along with sub-folders and document templates (.docx, .R, .Rmd and .sas). 
    The initial start.project function can be run from the R console or as a 
    local shiny app.
